dct_title_s: Kents restaurant in Atlantic City map, front
dct_description_sm: This map of Atlantic City is on one side of a tri-fold brochure for Kents Restaurant. Map specifically highlights locations of businesses run by Kents as well as specific parking areas and other notable landmarks. The quickest routes to the Kents establishments are bolded. There are also indexes of local hotels and churches.
